            <title>4 Key Tools for Predictive Maintenance</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	There are many different predictive maintenance tools available today, from infrared and vibration analyzers to dynamic and static analyzers. This 2-minute, 11-second video explains what each of these devices is designed to measure and how they can be used to make determinations about the condition of a motor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	     &lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/predictive_maintenance/~4/kGaYd5Qwkpg" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
