            </a10:author>
            <category>Videos</category>
            <category>Media Entries</category>
            <title>Owens Corning employee chooses Fluke thermal imaging for PdM</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	Hear what one Owens Corning employee says about how thermal imaging has helped them maintain their equipment, both electrical and mechanical, and why they chose Fluke thermal imagers to get the job done.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/predictive_maintenance/~4/gR2mEddwbrQ" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
            <a10:updated>2010-07-07T09:02:01-05:00</a10:updated>
            <a10:content type="text/html" src="http://reliableplant.com/View/25456/Owens-Corning-Fluke-PdM" />
