            <title>Why you need vibration analysis</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	Alan Richardson, president of Preventive Vibration Analysis Corporation, explains the importance and benefits of vibration analysis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/predictive_maintenance/~4/MtGnsxpSDVg" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
