            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:6d328db1-edcd-47c5-beaa-9d6400b80ffb</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/predictive_maintenance/~3/jdsrYc6v9PE/Powerful-ultrasound-PdM-pros</link>
