            <category>Media Entries</category>
            <title>Inspecting electrical cabinets with ultrasonic equipment</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;span&gt;This three-minute video explains how to use airborne ultrasound to scan for arcing, tracking, and corona discharge in MCC and other electrical cabinets. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/predictive_maintenance/~4/goklYQA_hN8" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
            <a10:updated>2010-02-22T15:53:49-06:00</a10:updated>
            <a10:content type="text/html" src="http://reliableplant.com/View/23000/Inspecting-cabinets-ultrasonic-equipment" />
