&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;This FLIR video explores predictive maintenance activities in production facilities, system failure prevention, and the safety of non-destructive testing. &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Access this 3-minute video by clicking on the link below.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/predictive_maintenance/~4/CjPnvzWj5ro" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
